title: THURSDAY 3/11 - Dak back in Big "D"
itunes:title: THURSDAY 3/11 - Dak back in Big "D"
description:
Dak Prescott and Jerry Jones spoke to the media Wednesday after the new deal became official (0:09). Speaking of quarterbacks, Panthers head coach Matt Rhule addressed the status of Teddy Bridgewater for the 2021 season (1:40), and the salary cap officially set at $182.5 million which came at the cost of some players being released (1:59)
